name: Gold AI Network Token
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
What is the project about?
Gain addresses the issue of failing reflection tokens using a first to market contract rewarding holders by investment amount in Eth, not on token holding.  So Reward whales are a thing of the past and rewards are fair.  Rewards are in PaxGold as GAIN is a gold trading project.

What makes your project unique?
Unique contract.
Partnership with a UK Ltd Company, Sandrock Capital company number 13389724.
GAIN owns a gold treasury which is traded and 80% profits are used to buy back and burn $GAIN.
Buy and own your own trading bots with full training.

History of your project.
Launched May 2023. Fair launch, no presales, 30k Liquidity.

What’s next for your project?
Report first trading profits
Launch NFTs where trading bots can be purchased by the community in cryptocurrency
Burn GAIN tokens

What can your token be used for?
Passive income in PAXOS GOLD ($PAXG)
